item.description: Come to Murphy's tap room Sep 18th at 7:30 to meet with Jared Chicoine, the NH Campaign manager. We'll be discussing the big walk with Ron Paul and his family on the 29th, and laying out a strategy. It's a great chance to find out what is going on in the campaign, and to socialize with fellow supporters.
item.name: Murphy's Taproom and Jared
